sections.heading: to 69-17-10 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1987, ch. 234, § 84 repealed 69-17-1 to 69-17-10 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1933, ch. 153, §§ 79 and 81 to 87 and as amended by Laws 1973, ch. 218, §§ 19 and 20, relating to underground haulage in coal mines, effective July 1, 1987. For present comparable provisions,see69-8-1 to 69-8-15 NMSA 1978.
